    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Working on this, got a fix (use the full url). The underlying issue is that as soon as you use a base href,  when you push relative things inside pushState or location.href then they are resolved to the base href tag.\n\nWhich can either:\n- result in a full page load (when using #)\n- result in a security issue (when using pushState)\n",
    "created_at": "2016-03-02T14:36:11Z",
