    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "This is my fix (really really durty)\n\nBe carefull, it's durty.\n\n...\n\nDid I told you it's durty ? Yes ?\n\n``` javascript\ninstantsearch.widgets.durtyFixPagination = function() {\n    return {\n        render: function render(options) {\n\n            setTimeout(function() {\n            var matches = document.querySelectorAll(\"#pagination a[href]\");\n            var urlBegin = window.location.protocol + '//' + window.location.hostname;\n            var urlSearchBegin = urlBegin + '/?';\n            angular.forEach(matches, function(a) {\n            if (urlSearchBegin === a.href.substr(0, urlSearchBegin.length)) {\n                a.href = urlBegin + window.location.pathname + a.href.substr(urlSearchBegin.length - 1);\n            }\n            });\n            console.info('pagination fix done');\n            }, 800);\n\n        }\n    };\n};\n\nsearch.addWidget(instantsearch.widgets.durtyFixPagination());\n```\n",
